Singleton class / pattern
==========================
In OOPS, a singleton class is a class that can have only one object (instance of the class) at a time.

Design Singleton
================
1. Make constructor as private
2. Write a public static method that has return type of object of this singleton class( Lazy initialization)

Difference between Normal and Singleton class
=============================================
1. For normal class we can use constructor whereas for Singleton class we can use getInstance() method for instantiation

